<DATELINE>
   ETHIOPIA
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
ANGOLAN government officials and their rebel Unita opponents arrived in
Addis Ababa yesterday for talks to end war raging across Angola, Reuter
reports from the Ethiopian capital.
Ethiopian officials said a four-man team of Unita generals had arrived and
